<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="/2023/03/29/polemique-autour-dune-oeuvre-de-miriam-cahn-la-justice-donne-raison-au-palais-de-tokyo/">Polémique autour d&rsquo;une œuvre de Miriam Cahn : la justice donne raison au Palais de Tokyo</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="/">lepays</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="86" class="elementor elementor-86">
									<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-5decfd5a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="5decfd5a" data-element_type="section">
